data.description: Welcome! Welcome! Welcome! To this beautiful yet charming, well maintained home that boast spacious 3 bedrooms 2 full bath, open concept living/dining room, granite countertops, tray ceiling, recess lighting, stainless steel appliances, ceramic tile flooring, 3 year old roof located in FLOOD ZONE X. The back yard is large enough for gatherings and much more. The outside porch is great for relaxation with a sip of your favorite beverage to add to the ambience of the day. Video surveillance/cameras are not included with the sale as well as the alarm system. Schedule your showing today and make this your home!
